      • withColumns

        public StoreOperation.Builder withColumns(Collection<String> columnNames)
        Add the names & order of the columns to be inserted. Order is implied by the order of the names in the Collection. NOTE:: As of Riak TS 1.4, this functionality is not implemented server-side, and any stored data is expected to be in the order of the table.
        Parameters:
        columnNames - The names of the columns to insert, and an implicit order.
        Returns:
        a reference to this object

      • withColumnDescriptions

        public StoreOperation.Builder withColumnDescriptions(Collection<? extends ColumnDescription> columns)
        Add the names & order of the columns to be inserted. Order is implied by the order of the ColumnDescriptions in the Collection. NOTE:: As of Riak TS 1.4, this functionality is not implemented server-side, and any stored data is expected to be in the order of the table.
        Parameters:
        columns - The ColumnDescriptions that contain a column name and an implicit order.
        Returns:
        a reference to this object
